  "name": "Charmed Life",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/light_07.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 2nd level, the swashbuckler gains a knack for getting out of trouble. Three times per day as an immediate action before attempting a saving throw, she can add her Charisma modifier to the result of the save. She must choose to do this before the roll is made.</p>\n<p>At 6th level and every 4 levels thereafter, the number of times she can do this per day increases by one (to a maximum of 7 times per day at 18th level).</p>"
